{
  "texts": [
    "In prognostic modelling, AI models predict the growth of infectious diseases on the basis of population density and travel patterns.",
    "Out of many, Metabiota is an important step in predicting outbreaks and providing a quantified impact assessment.",
    "AI has also made it much faster to Explore Therapeutics by analyzing big data for spotting potential treatments [175][176][177][178][179].",
    "For Example, Benevolent identifies drugs for several diseases using AI.",
    "AI can be applied in the design of vaccines to analyze genomic data and design customized vaccines."
  ]
}